flowRoot.flowPara: Panel state when a different language has been selected and is installed.
Pending status, primarily for when a language has been selected but there isn't an internet connection.
If the window isn't focused when a language download is complete, a notification is shown.

Admins should be able to install languages from Software (so they can be used by other users). Should list installed languages. Shouldn't be possible to remove the current language, and should warn if attempting to remove a language that is being used by another user.
